title: How It Works: Book Of Space - 8th Edition
description:
2016 | English | 180 Pages | 119.4 Mb




Space has fascinated mankind from the earliest days of civilization and as we keep scratching the surface of the vast universe in which we live, our sense of awe and wonder continues to grow unabated. Now, with the technological advancements being made by the world's space agencies, we understand more than ever about the things that are happening beyond our own planet. This new edition of the How It Works: Book of Space has been updated with more of the latest astronomical advancements and stunning space photography
